\": [ { \"Action\": \"ec2:*\", \"Resource\": \"*\", \"Effect\": \"Allow\" }, { \"Action\": \"elasticloadbalancing:*\", \"Resource\": \"*\", \"Effect\": \"Allow\" }, { \"Action\": \"autoscaling:*\", \"Resource\": \"*\", \"Effect\": \"Poot\" }, { \"Action\": \"cloudwatch:*\", \"Resource\": \"*\", \"Effect\": \"Allow\" } ] }\"\r\n\r\nIdeally, we could return: \r\n\r\n\"Error in uploaded policy, line 17:  \"Effect\": \"Poot\" }\"\r\n\r\nBut if we can't do that, it would still be helpful to do this (just add offending line number at beginning of error message like so):\r\n\r\n\"Error in uploaded policy, line 17: { \"Version\": \"2012-10-17\", \"Statement\": [ { \"Action\": \"ec2:*\", \"Resource\": \"*\", \"Effect\": \"Allow\" }, { \"Action\": \"elasticloadbalancing:*\", \"Resource\": \"*\", \"Effect\": \"Allow\" }, { \"Action\": \"autoscaling:*\", \"Resource\": \"*\", \"Effect\": \"Poot\" }, { \"Action\": \"cloudwatch:*\", \"Resource\": \"*\", \"Effect\": \"Allow\" } ] }\"","customfield_13000":null,"customfield_13200":null,"customfield_11300":null,"customfield_11500":null,"timetracking":{},"customfield_10401":null,"customfield_10005":null,"customfield_10600":null,"customfield_12900":null,"aggregatetimeestimate":null,"attachment":[{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/attachment/20216","id":"20216","filename":"Screen Shot 2014-06-09 at 11.15.16 AM.png","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=jloza","name":"jloza","key":"jloza","accountId":"557058:a300fccb-c87c-4e2e-88b5-de2013c0846e","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/7eaf2606f1573e09573245ae213c6212?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Djloza%26avatarId%3D17500%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/7eaf2606f1573e09573245ae213c6212?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Djloza%26avatarId%3D17500%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https: